                <h2>Description</h2>
                <p>Chef It Up is a culinary companion that helps users sift through a multitude of recipes to find the perfect match for their culinary skills, busy schedules, and more.
                <p>By offering a user-friendly interface, our application streamlines the process of dining recipes on Google that can be hindered by paywalls or pop-up ads, encouraging users to explore while having fun in the kitchen. </p>
                <p>Our application aims to be a versatile tool in meal planning and preparation. It goes beyond simple filtering, as it offers our users to save recipes they've tried. With an emphasis on personalization, Chef It Up ensures that your experience is unique and suited to your taste, making cooking at home more accessible and enjoyable.</p>
                </p>
                <h2>How To Use</h2>
                <p>Login to your account, making an account is fast and easy if you don't have one yet. Creating an account makes it easy to find the recipes you like by saving your previous recipes</p>
                <p>Once you're logged in, use the dropdown menus to filter our recipe database and find dishes that meet your exact specifications.</p>
                <p>Select one of the dishes from the results and follow the instructions to make the dish. Once you're done cooking and eating, you can save the dish to your profile if it's something you want to go back to!</p>
